<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sobre - Pequenos Exploradores</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@700;800&family=Fredoka:wght@400;700&family=Righteous&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aluno-redesign.css">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    
    /* Navbar links com mesmo espaçamento da home */
    .nav-links-redesign { margin-left: 130px !important; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
      background: #f0faf4;
      color: #1a3c2a;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero-sobre {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d9e46 0%, #1a7a34 50%, #0f5c26 100%);
      padding: 80px 60px 100px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 72px;
    }

    .hero-sobre::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px; right: -60px;
      width: 300px; height: 300px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .hero-sobre::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -80px; left: -40px;
      width: 250px; height: 250px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-sobre h1 {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 56px;
      color: white;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-sobre h1 span { color: #a8f0c0; }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .hero-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }

    /* SECTION */
    .section-sobre {
      padding: 80px 60px;
    }

    .section-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: #e8f8ee;
      color: #2a7d40;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-label::before {
      content: '';
      width: 8px; height: 8px;
      background: #3aaa50;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 42px;
      color: #1a3c2a;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .section-title span { color: #3aaa50; }

    /* WELCOME GRID */
    .welcome-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .welcome-text p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #3a5a45;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .welcome-highlights {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .highlight-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      background: white;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1.5px solid #c8eed6;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .highlight-item:hover {
      transform: translateX(4px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(58,170,80,0.12);
    }

    .highlight-icon {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .highlight-icon.green { background: #e8f8ee; }
    .highlight-icon.blue { background: #e3f2fd; }
    .highlight-icon.yellow { background: #fff8e1; }

    .highlight-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1a3c2a;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .highlight-text span {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b8c76;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* MASCOT */
    .mascot-visual {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .mascot-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 36px;
      border: 2px solid #c8eed6;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(58,170,80,0.1);
      position: relative;
    }

    .mascot-avatars {
      display: flex;
      gap: -10px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .mascot-avatar {
      width: 100px; height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 4px solid white;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #e8f8ee;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 48px;
    }

    .mascot-avatar + .mascot-avatar { margin-left: -20px; }

    .mascot-name {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #1a3c2a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mascot-desc {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #6b8c76;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .floating-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px; right: -12px;
      background: #3aaa50;
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .mascot-stats {
      margin-top: 24px; 
      padding-top: 20px; 
      border-top: 1.5px solid #c8eed6;
      display: flex; 
      gap: 24px; 
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .stat-item {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive; 
      font-size: 28px; 
      color: #3aaa50;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 12px; 
      color: #6b8c76; 
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .stat-divider {
      width: 1px; 
      background: #c8eed6;
    }

    /* LEVELS */
    .levels-section {
      background: #1a7a34;
      padding: 80px 60px;
    }

    .levels-section .section-title { color: white; }
    .levels-section .section-title span { color: #a8f0c0; }

    .section-center {
      text-align: center; 
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-center-sub {
      font-size: 17px; 
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); 
      max-width: 520px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      font-weight: 400; 
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .levels-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 48px auto 0;
    }

    .level-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      text-align: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      transition: transform 0.25s, background 0.25s;
    }

    .level-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }

    .level-medal {
      width: 72px; height: 72px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    .medal-silver {
      background: rgba(192,192,192,0.3);
    }

    .level-name {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 26px;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .level-desc {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features-section {
      background: #f0faf4;
      padding: 80px 60px;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 48px auto 0;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1.5px solid #c8eed6;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(58,170,80,0.13);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #e8f8ee;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .feature-title {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 19px;
      color: #1a3c2a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .feature-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b8c76;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .feature-card.highlighted {
      background: #e8f8ee;
    }

    .feature-card.highlighted .feature-icon {
      background: white;
    }

    /* MISSION */
    .mission-section {
      background: #0e6699;
      padding: 80px 60px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .mission-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px; left: -80px;
      width: 320px; height: 320px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .mission-wrapper {
      position: relative; 
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mission-quote {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 40px;
      color: white;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mission-quote span { color: #7dd3f8; }

    .mission-sub {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .ods-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      color: white;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .ods-dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #7dd3f8;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      background: #61b231;
      padding: 56px 60px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 -4px 16px rgba(97,178,49,0.28);
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .footer-brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 26px;
      color: white;
    }

    .footer-tagline {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-weight: 400;
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .footer-heading {
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', cursive;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .footer-link {
      display: block;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .footer-link:hover { color: white; }

    .footer-contact-email {
      color: #a8f0c0;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      padding-top: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .social-btn {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .social-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.28); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .welcome-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .levels-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-sobre h1 { font-size: 38px; }
      .section-sobre { padding: 60px 28px; }
      .hero-sobre { padding: 60px 28px 80px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav class="navbar-redesign">
  <section class="logo-redesign">
    <img src="/img/log.png" alt="Logo Pequenos Exploradores">
  </section>
  <section class="nav-links-redesign">
    <a class="nav-link-redesign" href="/">Início</a>
    <a class="nav-link-redesign active" href="/sobre">Sobre</a>
    <a class="nav-link-redesign" href="https://www.instagram.com/pequenos_.exploradores_?igsh=MWthZnZ6eG1xeDlxdw==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Contato</a>
  </section>
  <section class="nav-right-redesign">
    <a href="/aluno-login" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg,#7c3aed 100%, #7c3aed 100%); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.6em 1.5em; border-radius: 8px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.95em;">Seja uma escola parceira</a>
  </section>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero-sobre">
  <section class="hero-badge">Educação Ambiental Infantil</section>
  <h1>Bem-vindo ao<br><span>Pequenos Exploradores!</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Uma aventura digital que une diversão, aprendizado e amor pela natureza para crianças de 4 a 10 anos.</p>
  <section class="hero-tags">
    <span class="hero-tag">🌱 Sustentabilidade</span>
    <span class="hero-tag">🎮 Gamificação</span>
    <span class="hero-tag">🦋 Fauna & Flora</span>
    <span class="hero-tag">🏫 Para Escolas</span>
  </section>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
<section class="section-sobre" style="background: white;">
  <section class="welcome-grid">
    <section class="welcome-text">
      <section class="section-label">Sobre o Projeto</section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Aprender é uma <span>grande aventura!</span></h2>
      <p>Aqui você vai descobrir os segredos da natureza de um jeito divertido, com jogos, desafios, vídeos e muitas descobertas incríveis.</p>
      <p>Ao longo da jornada, você vai explorar o mundo ao lado de <strong>Clarinha</strong> e <strong>Kauezinho</strong>, conhecendo os animais, as florestas, a água e aprendendo como cuidar do nosso planeta.</p>
      <section class="welcome-highlights">
        <section class="highlight-item">
          <section class="highlight-icon green">🌿</section>
          <section class="highlight-text">
            <strong>Conteúdo lúdico e interativo</strong>
            <span>Atividades que unem diversão e conhecimento ambiental</span>
          </section>
        </section>
        <section class="highlight-item">
          <section class="highlight-icon blue">🏆</section>
          <section class="highlight-text">
            <strong>Sistema de recompensas</strong>
            <span>Moedinhas virtuais que incentivam o progresso</span>
          </section>
        </section>
        <section class="highlight-item">
          <section class="highlight-icon yellow">📚</section>
          <section class="highlight-text">
            <strong>Apoio pedagógico completo</strong>
            <span>Ferramenta para educadores aplicarem em sala de aula</span>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section class="mascot-visual">
      <section class="mascot-card">
        <span class="floating-badge">🌟 Personagens</span>
        <section class="mascot-avatars">
          <section class="mascot-avatar"><img src="/img/Kau.jpeg" alt="Kauezinho" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;"></section>
          <section class="mascot-avatar"><img src="/img/Cla.jpeg" alt="Clarinha" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;"></section>
        </section>
        <section class="mascot-name">Kauezinho & Clarinha</section>
        <section class="mascot-desc">Seus guias nessa jornada<br>de exploração e descoberta!</section>
        <section class="mascot-stats">
          <section class="stat-item">
            <section class="stat-number">PQ</section>
            <section class="stat-label">Pequenos Exploradores</section>
          </section>
          <section class="stat-divider"></section>
          <section class="stat-item">
            <section class="stat-number" style="color: #0e6699;">ODS 15</section>
            <section class="stat-label">Vida Terrestre</section>
          </section>
          <section class="stat-divider"></section>
          <section class="stat-item">
            <section class="stat-number" style="color: #e6a817;">30</section>
            <section class="stat-label">níveis</section>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
    </section>
  </section>
</section>

<!-- LEVELS -->
<section class="levels-section">
  <section class="section-center">
    <section class="section-label" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Jornada de aprendizado</section>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: white;">Evolua em três <span>níveis incríveis</span></h2>
    <p class="section-center-sub">A cada atividade concluída, novas conquistas são desbloqueadas!</p>
  </section>
  <section class="levels-grid">
    <section class="level-card">
      <section class="level-medal">🥉</section>
      <section class="level-name">Bronze</section>
      <section class="level-desc">Dê os primeiros passos na sua jornada ambiental. Conheça os personagens e explore o mundo natural.</section>
    </section>
    <section class="level-card" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16);">
      <section class="level-medal medal-silver">🥈</section>
      <section class="level-name">Prata</section>
      <section class="level-desc">Aprofunde seus conhecimentos sobre fauna, flora e práticas sustentáveis do dia a dia.</section>
    </section>
    <section class="level-card">
      <section class="level-medal">🥇</section>
      <section class="level-name">Ouro</section>
      <section class="level-desc">Torne-se um verdadeiro Pequeno Explorador! Domine os desafios e seja um guardião do planeta.</section>
    </section>
  </section>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features-section">
  <section class="section-center">
    <section class="section-label">O que você vai encontrar</section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Uma plataforma <span>cheia de recursos!</span></h2>
  </section>
  <section class="features-grid">
    <section class="feature-card">
      <section class="feature-icon">🎬</section>
      <section class="feature-title">Vídeos Educativos</section>
      <section class="feature-desc">Conteúdos que ensinam sobre o meio ambiente de forma leve e envolvente</section>
    </section>
    <section class="feature-card">
      <section class="feature-icon">🎯</section>
      <section class="feature-title">Atividades Interativas</section>
      <section class="feature-desc">Experiências práticas que estimulam o aprendizado ativo das crianças</section>
    </section>
    <section class="feature-card">
      <section class="feature-icon">🧩</section>
      <section class="feature-title">Quizzes & Desafios</section>
      <section class="feature-desc">Jogos que reforçam o conhecimento adquirido de forma divertida</section>
    </section>
    <section class="feature-card">
      <section class="feature-icon">🪙</section>
      <section class="feature-title">Recompensas</section>
      <section class="feature-desc">Moedinhas virtuais trocadas por brindes educativos e conquistas</section>
    </section>
    <section class="feature-card">
      <section class="feature-icon">🦜</section>
      <section class="feature-title">Fauna & Flora</section>
      <section class="feature-desc">Conteúdos sobre animais e natureza para conectar as crianças ao planeta</section>
    </section>
    <section class="feature-card highlighted">
      <section class="feature-icon">👩‍🏫</section>
      <section class="feature-title">Para Educadores</section>
      <section class="feature-desc">Recursos pedagógicos para apoiar professores em sala de aula</section>
    </section>
  </section>
</section>

<!-- MISSION -->
<section class="mission-section">
  <section class="mission-wrapper">
    <section class="section-label" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Nossa missão</section>
    <section class="mission-quote">"Explorar, aprender e <span>cuidar</span> — juntos por um planeta melhor."</section>
    <p class="mission-sub">O Pequenos Exploradores é um instrumento de transformação social, inspirando crianças a se tornarem protagonistas do cuidado com o planeta.</p>
    <section class="ods-chip">
      <span class="ods-dot"></span>
      Alinhado à ODS 15 da ONU — Vida Terrestre
    </section>
